{"tid":735131,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「發達大計」有冇諗過二八定律可以用黎賭波？","createTime":"2018-07-09T08:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T02:35:18.000Z","uid":123335,"like":12,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"98f00c0307c4ea2c6f23a6403332140188d56507","tid":735131,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:50:16.000Z","msg":"帕累托法則（英語：Pareto principle），（也被稱為 80/20 法則, 是重要的少數的法則，也是因素稀疏的原則） 指出，約有 80％ 的影響來自於 20％ 的原因 。管理諮詢 約瑟夫&middot;朱蘭在義大利與經濟學家 帕累托提出這一原則, 並在1896年 洛桑大學 注意到80/20的聯繫，並在他的第一篇文章「 政治經濟學「上顯示帕累托，義大利約有80％的土地由20％的人口所有;帕累托透過觀察到他的花園中約有20％的豌豆株上產出了80％的豌豆 <br />\n<br />\n而應用係賭博上<br />\n80%贏返黎既錢，好大可能落係20%既注碼身上<br />\n<br />\n假設你賭本有$100 ，每局平注$10 <br />\n你好大機會靠兩場（共$20賭本，買賠率6倍 = 變$120 ）<br />\n<br />\n而其他八場都係輸錢 （= 輸晒$80 賭金）<br />\n<br />\n最終會做到本金既120%增長<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我依家拎$500 出黎做實驗，平注$50<br />\n買賠率接近6倍既盤 <br />\n就會做到本金120%增長<br />\n<br />\n$500*1.2^38 = 51萬<br />\n<br />\n咁就可以賺到我人生第一桶金<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/09/164940_e849a6ed9e7a3150091d3e2b6077212f.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F09%2F164940_e849a6ed9e7a3150091d3e2b6077212f.jpeg&h=50f278da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/09/164940_42938f32fbdf999121e4b23ba509723f.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F09%2F164940_42938f32fbdf999121e4b23ba509723f.jpeg&h=712a3c6f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a31e2744c24b5e2b58cfcb4efb2e2710dc5c9ac3","tid":735131,"uid":123335,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:58:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/09/165823_d5c2b3a2591ca37d8a5b0a9134b948b8.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F09%2F165823_d5c2b3a2591ca37d8a5b0a9134b948b8.jpeg&h=1580634c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"21f5084a4661821e2a14915a9f7c951063d792f6","tid":735131,"uid":66496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T09:00:55.000Z","msg":"留名睇表演<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a6db2a09cc852af922d471cb5f9e4f950237ce3","tid":735131,"uid":10913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T09:01:55.000Z","msg":"傻閪"},{"pid":"81a6a5ce8c62e0ac6da54678f5ce8e9fdbe8e686","tid":735131,"uid":54486,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T09:03:15.000Z","msg":"咁你不如買99倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e6da97bf13fad79d6734337feefd4a007f80438","tid":735131,"uid":54486,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T09:04:19.000Z","msg":"6.5 賠率既是你要買6.5舖先中一舖，你覺得會有20%(1/5) 命中？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f77e3bc7a94ada12e1fe409c653ef9d10c028e9","tid":735131,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T09:11:02.000Z","msg":"痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8294859c22214936040ee7a1eb979dd2ca40988c","tid":735131,"uid":123335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T09:19:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/09/171905_65dd5de8ae8ae31db563c4f387163b6e.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F09%2F171905_65dd5de8ae8ae31db563c4f387163b6e.jpeg&h=29c65699&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f5e1322dfaa82376d71f1f533415c2556aa59e66","tid":735131,"uid":134128,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T09:21:12.000Z","msg":"你條友上次第一場就被馬會收皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"